data.description:
~*~ This Immaculately kept 4-bed / 4-bath, Full partially finished Basement and Oversized 2-Car garage, YES.. Two 4-door trucks will fit! Covered Front Porch and Back Patio. 
This Open concept Ranch style home with natural light, tall Ceilings, showcasing exquisite upgrades including Granite counter tops, hardwood floors, Vaulted ceilings and stylish finishes throughout. The gourmet chefs kitchen boasts high-end stainless appliances, Double-ovens, Granite countertops, (2)-Islands, Five burner gas cook top, Pot filler, A plethora of rich solid wood cabinets that provide tons of storage, A butlers pantry, built-in Office, Mudroom and so much MORE! The Bright Primary Suite with Coffered ceilings, 5-piece Bath, Soaking tub, Glass Shower with Huge walk-in Closet. The Jr. Suite boasts high ceilings, a 3/4 Bath & Walk-in Closet. A bonus Room-(Music, Sitting, 2nd Office), Formal Dining rm.with Wainscoting finishes out the Main Floor of this expansive Home.
The Basement, with garden level egress windows for a bright area. Stroll down the Staircase to the Finished Large Family room, Bed #3 and Bed #4- the 2nd. J.R. Suite with 3/4 Bath- Glass block shower, Rain head and stone floor. There's still over a 1000sq. ft. of unfinished basement for you to finish to your Design..(Craft Rm., Gym, Man Cave, More Bed Rooms?) 
The Back Yard to entertain friends & family with covered concrete Patio, Grass & Turf, Block wall, Plumbed gas for the BBQ. 
 The home is located on a peaceful street close to the Community Club house & Pool, Parks and Open space, with easy access to all the Amenities of Parker, CO. Top-rated Restaurants, Schools- (public & private), Breweries, Coffee shops, Grocery stores, Yoga/fitness studios. This is the Home you are looking for, Call US for your Showing today...
